<l>kāma meṉavoṉṟu kaṇṇiṉṟeṉ ṉeñcattai </l>
<l> yāmattu māḷun toḻil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even at midnight is my mind worried by lust, and this one thing, alas! is without mercy.</l>
